parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to replace the Takata airbag inflators can cause the airbag to deploy incorrectly, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: "Service Airbag" message appears on the dashboard
airbag deploys without warning or impact
airbag warning indicator flashes near the front passenger side.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unavailable Replacement Parts for Takata Airbag Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of replacement parts for the Takata airbag recall can cause a delay in the repair, leaving the vehicle owner at risk of injury or death due to the faulty airbag.
symptoms: Dealer informs customer that replacement parts are not available
customer is unable to schedule repair due to unavailability of parts
customer is told to wait for parts to become available.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Deployment without Warning or Impact
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag deploying without warning or impact can cause serious injury or death to the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbag deploys without warning or impact
side and rear airbags deploy without warning or impact.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various malfunctions, including loss of power steering, stalling, and loss of control, which can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: door locks locking and unlocking on their own
and defrost turning on and off
service stability traction control and service stability rack warning indicators illuminating
windows rolling up or down without warning
rear doors not locking and unlocking with remote
rear passenger lock not unlocking from key or button
navigation CD ejecting and inserting itself automatically
lights on the instrument panel and center console flickering

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Low Oil Pressure and Engine Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Low oil pressure can cause engine failure, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Low oil pressure causing engine failure

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control can cause loss of control, which can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: suddenly failing when another electrical device is activated
windows rolling up or down without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door locks and unlocks can cause inconvenience, distraction, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Rear doors not locking and unlocking with remote
rear passenger lock not unlocking from key or button
doors locking and unlocking on their own.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the electronic power steering system can cause loss of control, accidents, or fatalities, especially at high speeds or when navigating curves.
symptoms: corrosion of the power steering unit
